    "source": "## Production Notes\n\nFor production deployment:\n\n1. **Use Eventstream** for ingestion from Event Hub\n2. **Configure proper watermarks** based on expected latency\n3. **Set up checkpointing** to reliable storage\n4. **Monitor stream lag** via Spark UI\n5. **Configure alerts** for processing delays\n6. **Use Eventhouse/KQL** for sub-second queries"
